reviewText: Disappointed and very poor video quality. It's now collecting dust on my dresser.

I can't be upset, I paid less than six dollars, and it's a couple of hard working kids just trying to make a video to teach... they're undoubtedly knowledgeable... pretty sure they've had that girl playing since she could walk.

But despite the fun little cartoon characters on the cover and all the simple children's songs, this isn't really a video for little kids...
